Nyalakan mesin bom!

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:20.400
Siapkan luncuran!

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:22.480
Iya, Kak Alvida!

00:05:22.700 --> 00:05:23.960
Tidak ada gesekan…

00:05:26.820 --> 00:05:28.680
Sube Sube Spur!

00:05:34.530 --> 00:05:36.730
Jangan biarkan bajak laut lolos!

00:05:43.140 --> 00:05:44.920
Asap apa ini?

